Erlang Hotline client with a web UI.

You need erlang, and rebar

1. Make a file in apps/hotline/priv/conf/local.conf that looks like this:

{connection_default_hostname, <<"livebus.org">>}.
{connection_default_title,    <<"Livebus">>}.
{connection_default_name,     <<"Nickname">>}.
{connection_default_username, <<"username">>}.
{connection_default_password, <<"password">>}.
{connection_default_icon,     150}.

2. Start the app with ./start.sh

3. Point a browser at http://localhost:55500/

---

Wiki on the Hotline protocol: http://hotline.wikia.com/wiki/Hotline_Wiki
